{"tid":1120980,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"晤各國代表  習近平：國家間不能動輒以武力威脅","createTime":"2019-04-23T04:56:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-23T13:20:39.000Z","uid":184679,"like":1,"dislike":45,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"1d9db70d6c3ad0cab260ff5d4972d94adfae79fd","tid":1120980,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T04:56:52.000Z","msg":"23日上午10時20分許，國家主席、中央軍委主席習近平在青島國際會議中心同應邀前來參加活動的多國海軍代表團團長集體合影留念。<br />\n<br />\n習近平之後發表講話，指中國海軍將一如既往同各國海軍加強交流合作；他還表示，國家間要有事多商量、有事好商量，不能動輒就訴諸武力或以武力相威脅。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B/320912/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E6%B5%B7%E8%BB%8D70%E5%91%A8%E5%B9%B4-%E7%BF%92%E8%BF%91%E5%B9%B3%E6%99%A4%E5%90%84%E5%9C%8B%E4%BB%A3%E8%A1%A8-%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%B6%E9%96%93%E4%B8%8D%E8%83%BD%E5%8B%95%E8%BC%92%E4%BB%A5%E6%AD%A6%E5%8A%9B%E5%A8%81%E8%84%85\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%2F320912%2F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%25B5%25B7%25E8%25BB%258D70%25E5%2591%25A8%25E5%25B9%25B4-%25E7%25BF%2592%25E8%25BF%2591%25E5%25B9%25B3%25E6%2599%25A4%25E5%2590%2584%25E5%259C%258B%25E4%25BB%25A3%25E8%25A1%25A8-%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E9%2596%2593%25E4%25B8%258D%25E8%2583%25BD%25E5%258B%2595%25E8%25BC%2592%25E4%25BB%25A5%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E5%258A%259B%25E5%25A8%2581%25E8%2584%2585&d=%2BBr8udGLiiUmorY0Hhmb0kcTp%2BQsjpNju1TtMRGBB4E%3D&h=078dc5c9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B/320912/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E6%B5%B7%E8%BB%8D70%E5%91%A8%E5%B9%B4-%E7%BF%92%E8%BF%91%E5%B9%B3%E6%99%A4%E5%90%84%E5%9C%8B%E4%BB%A3%E8%A1%A8-%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%B6%E9%96%93%E4%B8%8D%E8%83%BD%E5%8B%95%E8%BC%92%E4%BB%A5%E6%AD%A6%E5%8A%9B%E5%A8%81%E8%84%85</a>"},{"pid":"83659387c5d83572477bd76f554f56840bd83108","tid":1120980,"uid":50457,"like":37,"dislike":3,"score":34,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T04:57:50.000Z","msg":"台灣，中國之間不是國家之間<img src=\"/asse